---
import StaticLayout from '../layouts/StaticLayout.astro';
---

<StaticLayout title="Contact Us" description="Get in touch with the UtilityDocker team. Report bugs, request features, or ask questions.">
  <p>
    We'd love to hear from you! Whether you have a feature request, found a bug, or just want to say hello,
    here's how to reach us.
  </p>

  <h2>Report a Bug</h2>
  <p>
    If a tool isn't working as expected, please let us know. Include the tool name, your browser,
    and what you expected to happen vs. what actually happened.
  </p>

  <h2>Request a Tool</h2>
  <p>
    Have an idea for a tool you'd like to see? We're always looking for new tools to add.
    The best suggestions are specific and describe a real problem you're trying to solve.
  </p>

  <h2>Email</h2>
  <p>
    Reach us at <strong>hello@utilitydocker.com</strong>
  </p>
</StaticLayout>
